OL,3,CDolly Parton cancels Las Vegas shows:
OL,4,C'I need to rebuild my engine'
OL,6,FSinger Dolly Parton has said she is
OL,7,F"truly sorry" after cancelling a
OL,8,Fseries of Las Vegas shows due to
OL,9,Fhealth issues.
OL,11,FThe 80-year-old was due to perform a
OL,12,Fsix-show residency at Caesar's Palace
OL,13,Fin September, but in a social media
OL,14,Fvideo, she said she was receiving
OL,15,Fmedication that made her "a little bit
OL,16,Fswimmy headed".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
