OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778008271
OL,3,CDolly Parton cancels Las Vegas shows:
OL,4,C'I need to rebuild my engine'
OL,6,FParton also revealed she had been
OL,7,Fstruggling with kidney stones and that
OL,8,Fher immune and digestive systems "had
OL,9,Fgot all out of whack" over the last
OL,10,Ffew years.
OL,12,FThe 9 to 5 singer had previously been
OL,13,Fscheduled to perform the concerts in
OL,14,FDecember 2025, before postponing them
OL,15,Funtil September.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
