PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778008271
OL,3,CDolly Parton cancels Las Vegas shows:
OL,4,C'I need to rebuild my engine'
OL,6,FBut in the video posted on Instagram
OL,7,Fon Monday evening, Parton said: "I'm
OL,8,Fresponding really well to meds and
OL,9,Ftreatments and I'm improving every
OL,10,Fday," and that doctors had assured her
OL,11,Fthat "everything I have is treatable."
OL,13,FHowever, she added that, "it's going
OL,14,Fto take me a little while before I'm
OL,15,Fup to stage performance level."
OL,17,FShe asked fans to think of her like an
OL,18,F"old classic car, that once restored
OL,19,Fcan be better than ever.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
