OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1778008271
OL,3,CDolly Parton cancels Las Vegas shows:
OL,4,C'I need to rebuild my engine'
OL,6,F"When they raised the hood on this old
OL,7,Fantique, they realised that I need to
OL,8,Frebuild my engine."
OL,10,FShe apologised to fans who were due to
OL,11,Fsee her, saying: "I am truly sorry
OL,12,Fthat I'm going to miss all of you that
OL,13,Fhad tickets to see me in Las Vegas."
