OL,3,CDolly Parton cancels Las Vegas shows:
OL,4,C'I need to rebuild my engine'
OL,6,FLast October, Parton was forced to
OL,7,Fdispel rumours she was seriously ill,
OL,8,Fafter her sister said she had been "up
OL,9,Fall night praying" for the singer.
OL,11,FIn a video titled 'I Ain't Dead Yet!'
OL,12,Fshe said: "Everybody thinks that I am
OL,13,Fsicker than I am. Do I look sick to
OL,14,Fyou?!"
OL,16,FShe added: "I wanted to put
OL,17,Feverybody's mind at ease, those of you
OL,18,Fthat seem to be real concerned, which
OL,19,FI appreciate, and I appreciate your
OL,20,Fprayers because I'm a person of faith."
